title: Pink Floyd - The Dark Side of the Moon SACD - FLAC
description:
Thought by many to be the best album of all time, The Dark Side of the Moon by Pink Flyod (or jokingly referred to as "Stink Floyd" by my friends) transcends time. I&#039;ve felt that the SACD edition of this has needed a good and proper upload in the beloved FLAC format. On this version, you&#039;ll likely hear things you missed on the CD (or even vinyl) version. It&#039;s an amazing disc.

 I&#039;ve decided to upload it like this because no one really has any DTS compatible devices, so for the sake of everyone (minus the FLAC ignorant,) you&#039;ll get this equally speaker filling version. 

I will seed this puppy to my max at around 200kb/s tops. Once/if this torrent takes off, I shall drop it a bit for my sake.

If you&#039;d like to convert this, I recommend FLAC Frontend: http://flac.sourceforge.net/download.html

The program shall convert the files to WAV. From there, use whatever media player you please. I personally keep my files at a nice 256kbps VBR AAC format. 


1 	Speak to Me
2 	Breathe
3 	On the Run
4 	Time
5 	The Great Gig in the Sky
6 	Money
7 	Us and Them
8 	Any Colour You Like
9 	Brain Damage
10 	Eclipse

For every person that doesn&#039;t seed, one angel shall contract hepatitis.

Every person that does seed will receive a liberal amount of hugs.

~VIVA PIRACY!
